Cosponsored by Representatives: ARCHER of Saco, BELL of Yarmouth, BRIDGEO of
Augusta, CARLOW of Buxton, LYMAN of Livermore Falls, MONTELL of Gardiner,
ROLLINS of Augusta.
Printed on recycled paper

1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 Sec. 1. 20-A MRSA §1, sub-§20-B is enacted to read:
3 20-B. Personal finance. "Personal finance" means a course of study including
4 instruction in the applications of money in areas such as saving, investing, banking and the
