3344 This bill requires that all secondary schools include one year of personal finance as part
3355 of the mathematics instruction required to obtain a high school diploma. It changes the
3366 minimum requirement for a high school diploma from 2 years of mathematics or the
3377 equivalent in standards achievement to 3 years of mathematics or the equivalent in
3388 standards achievement.
